---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about Evaloc's 40+ years of water conservation expertise and meet our dedicated team.">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="page-label">Our Story</span>
      <h1>About Evaloc</h1>
      <p>Pioneering water conservation technology since 1983</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission-grid">
        <div class="mission-content">
          <span class="section-label">Our Mission</span>
          <h2>Conserving Earth's Most Precious Resource</h2>
          <p>
            Water is the most widely used, profoundly essential, and abundantly available yet increasingly scarce
            commodity on Earth. Without it, life is impossible.
          </p>
          <p>
            Since 1950, freshwater resources have been under ever-increasing pressure due to population growth,
            industrialization, and climate change. Evaporation from open water bodies accounts for billions of
            liters lost annually.
          </p>
          <p>
            At Evaloc, we've dedicated over four decades to developing and perfecting a proven solution to
            reduce water evaporation loss by up to 35% from any stationary water body. Our patented, non-toxic
            technology has saved over 17 billion liters of water since 1983.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-visual">
          <div class="mission-stats">
            <div class="mission-stat">
              <span class="number">1983</span>
              <span class="label">Founded</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mission-stat">
              <span class="number">40+</span>
              <span class="label">Years Experience</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mission-stat">
              <span class="number">17B+</span>
              <span class="label">Liters Saved</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mission-stat">
              <span class="number">150+</span>
              <span class="label">Projects</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- History Section -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Our Journey</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">A Legacy of Innovation</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          From pioneering research to widespread adoption, our journey in water conservation spans four decades.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">1960s</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Global Research Begins</h3>
            <p>Evaporation retarding experiments gain worldwide attention. Various methods are tested including water coloring, wind barriers, and floating covers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">1983</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Evaloc is Born</h3>
            <p>Mr. Shirish Patwardhan invents the Evaloc water evaporation retardant and patented usage method, beginning commercial deployment in India.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">1990s</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Government Adoption</h3>
            <p>Central and State government agencies begin using Evaloc for municipal water conservation projects across India.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">2000s</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Industrial Expansion</h3>
            <p>Major corporations including L&T, Adani, JSW, and others adopt Evaloc for their industrial water storage needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">2020s</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Global Reach</h3>
            <p>With OECD certification and EU compliance, Evaloc is now available for projects in Western Central Asia, Africa, Europe, America and Australia continents, experiencing water shortage due to high evaporation rates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Our Team</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Meet the People Behind Evaloc</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          A family-run business with deep expertise in water conservation and manufacturing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card featured">
          <div class="team-photo shirish-photo">
            <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/team/shirish.png`} alt="Shirish Patwardhan" class="team-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <h3>Shirish Patwardhan</h3>
            <span class="role">Founder & Inventor</span>
            <p>
              Inventor of the Evaloc Water Evaporation Retardant and patented usage methods (Evaloc SRP, SFMDA, MPDT).
              Consultant to Central & State Government projects, companies, and NGOs. Over 40 years of experience
              in water storage, balancing, conservation, and optimal usage.
            </p>
            <ul class="achievements">
              <li>Hundreds of successful projects since 1983</li>
              <li>Patent holder for product and method</li>
              <li>Government consultant</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo supriya-photo">
            <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/team/supriya.png`} alt="Supriya Patwardhan" class="team-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <h3>Supriya Patwardhan</h3>
            <span class="role">Partner - Manufacturing</span>
            <p>35 years of experience in manufacturing process management and quality control.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo vishal-photo">
            <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/team/vishal.png`} alt="Vishal Patwardhan" class="team-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <h3>Vishal Patwardhan</h3>
            <span class="role">Partner - Operations</span>
            <p>15 years of experience in manufacturing process and on-site operations management.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo jui-photo">
            <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/team/jui.png`} alt="Jui Patwardhan" class="team-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <h3>Jui Patwardhan</h3>
            <span class="role">Partner - Administration</span>
            <p>6 years of experience in manufacturing process and business administration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Info -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="company-grid">
        <div class="company-card">
          <h3>AquaSavio</h3>
          <p>The brand name under which Evaloc products and services are marketed and delivered.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="company-card">
          <h3>SP WaterEver LLP</h3>
          <p>The corporate entity responsible for manufacturing, distribution, and project implementation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="company-card">
          <h3>Registered & Patented</h3>
          <p>Both the Evaloc product and application method are officially registered and patent-protected.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Partner With Us</h2>
        <p>Join the hundreds of organizations conserving water with Evaloc technology.</p>
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/contact`} class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Get In Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 10rem 0 5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .page-label {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mission-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .mission-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mission-stat {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission-stat .number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .mission-stat .label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 80px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 80px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: right;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-marker::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    right: -1.35rem;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid white;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Team Section */
  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .team-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }

  .team-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
  }

  .team-card.featured {
    grid-column: span 3;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
  }

  .team-photo {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Individual photo adjustments */
  .shirish-photo .team-img {
    max-width: 100%;
    transform: scale(1.15);
  }

  .supriya-photo .team-img {
    max-width: 240px;
  }

  .vishal-photo .team-img {
    max-width: 240px;
    transform: scale(0.8);
  }

  .jui-photo {
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .jui-photo .team-img {
    max-width: 220px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .photo-placeholder {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
  }

  .team-img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 320px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .team-card:not(.featured) .team-photo {
    height: 200px;
  }

  .team-card:not(.featured) .photo-placeholder {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .team-card:not(.featured) .team-img {
    max-width: 280px;
  }

  .team-info {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .team-info h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .team-info .role {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .team-info p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .achievements {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .achievements li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .achievements li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  /* Company Grid */
  .company-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .company-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .company-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .company-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .mission-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .team-card.featured {
      grid-column: span 1;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .team-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .company-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline::before {
      left: 20px;
    }

    .timeline-marker {
      width: 40px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline-marker::after {
      right: -1rem;
    }

    .page-header {
      padding: 8rem 0 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
